<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.1">
<l>kaiyilaṅ kāḻi caṅkaṉ karumukil tiruni ṟattaṉ</l>
<l>poyyilaṉ meyyaṉ tantā ḷaṭaivarē laṭimai yākkum</l>
<l>ceyyalar kamala mōṅku ceṟipoḻil teṉti ruppēr</l>
<l>paiyara vaṇaiyāṉ nāmam paravinā ṉuynta vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way I was saved was by spreading the name of</l>
<l rend="indent">the one with the shining discus and conch in hand,</l>
<l>The one whose divine hue is of a dark cloud, the one who is truth,</l>
<l rend="indent">who is not false,</l>
<l>The one whose bed is a hooded serpent in Tiruppēr of the South</l>
<l rend="indent">with tall, thick groves [and] lotuses which grow in the fields,</l>
<l>Who takes [everyone] into service if they take refuge at his feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
